{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","data":{"alias":"cuddlesome-titanous-seamonkey","description":"## Reproduction Steps\n1. Install the agents extra + ANTHROPIC_API_KEY; 2. invoke the live eval path run_eval('plan-review-novelty') (src/rebar/llm/evals/eval.py) as docs/plan-review-gate.md suggests ('the discriminates_novelty eval remains available to re-run'); 3. observe eval_solver.run_case (src/rebar/llm/evals/eval_solver.py:156) raise ValueError for every dataset case.\n\nExpected: the plan-review-novelty prompt's discriminates_novelty gold set runs live and reports per-case verdicts. Actual: run_case dispatches only criterion ids (_criterion_id), code-review prompt ids (_code_review_prompt_id), and the three hardcoded agentic reviewers (completion-verifier / ticket-quality / spec-alignment); plan-review-novelty matches none, so the eval cannot execute and the gate-doc claim is hollow.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] eval_solver.run_case dispatches plan-review-novelty cases to the novelty scorer path (score_novelty with a case-supplied prior-findings set), returning per-case scoreable output.\n- [ ] The discriminates_novelty gold set runs end-to-end live: the eval completes with per-case verdicts (no ValueError), demonstrated by a recorded run.\n- [ ] A unit test pins the dispatch (a plan-review-novelty case routed offline via FakeRunner does not raise).","id":"ba85-4149-8049-45a7","parent_id":"","priority":2,"tags":[],"ticket_type":"bug","title":"discriminates_novelty eval is not live-runnable: no plan-review-novelty dispatch arm in eval_solver.run_case"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1784097366169512001,"uuid":"51d9d951-1fb8-43e4-9b5b-cef01f7b6f82"}